e Pain de Sucre</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="1">Sucré <x id="1"/> Pâtisserie Pain de Sucre</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="1">Dulce <x id="1"/> Pastelería Pain de Sucre</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="1" conf="Translated" origin="tm" origin-system="PainDeSucre" percent="84"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">+Q6sBfl60ZtDEoU0YMciY+CkEUCO+RXQQq+zbDWv+6g=</sdl:value><sdl:value key="created_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="created_on">01/15/2025 23:15:32</sdl:value><sdl:value key="last_modified_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="modified_on">01/15/2025 23:15:32</sdl:value><sdl:value key="FuzzyMatchRepair">true</sdl:value><sdl:value key="SDL:OriginalTranslationHash">176361721</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="6"/></sdl:cxts><trans-unit translate="no" id="7ea31c2d-e821-4fd3-b6ed-bc4903fb765e"><source/></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="7"/></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="43cad8ab-dd2a-4183-9a34-c45e21fa24be"><source>Notre expérience de pâtissiers dans la restauration nous fait aborder le sucre comme un assaisonnement, ce qui explique que nos créations soient peu sucrées.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="2">Notre expérience de pâtissiers dans la restauration nous fait aborder le sucre comme un assaisonnement, ce qui explique que nos créations soient peu sucrées.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="2">Gracias a nuestra experiencia en la restauración como reposteros, empleamos el azúcar como un aderezo, lo cual explica que nuestras creaciones sean poco dulzonas.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="2" conf="Translated" origin="interactive"><sdl:rep id="t77f3NzShE+27pLm8u52UzQ+g/xtuoFNIZQ5kZIrC1o="/><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">t77f3NzShE+27pLm8u52UzQ+g/xtuoFNIZQ5kZIrC1o=</sdl:value><sdl:value key="created_by">SARAS\saram</sdl:value><sdl:value key="created_on">01/16/2025 18:50:00</sdl:value><sdl:value key="last_modified_by"